      "comment": "EMPEROR ZULU (2) ran good time (23.01) when finishing third in a Grade 5 at this track after overcoming a collision in the run. Has the ability and expected to go close. BLACKPOOL VIPER (1) collided in the run and missed the frame when fifth (22.95) at this track over 400m in a Grade 5. Must include in calculations. WAVE OF FUN (7) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 1.5 lengths into second (22.97) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Deserves a win and gets her chance. HUGO GUNDI (8) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
